DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260330T094500
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=MO,TH
SUMMARY:Soft drink bottler window
DESCRIPTION:Check the supplier board, flavour holds, and cooler recovery against the bottler visit.
